    "headline": "Greg Abel Has Been Leading Berkshire for 100 Days. Things Are Already Changing.",
    "summary": "On a cold afternoon in December, as  Greg Abel  was days away from taking the reins of  Berkshire Hathaway  he took questions from employees at a weekly staff luncheon.  One asked if he was going to move the company out of Omaha, Neb., its headquarters for decades during  Warren Buffett’s  run as leader.  No, Abel said, there would be no move.",
